{"tid":433028,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【仲以為斷正】質問「做緊咩呀你！」 女經理誤會員工面都紅埋","createTime":"2017-10-12T04:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T05:21:10.000Z","uid":3189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d3327c98528c1d2fa3697e7302988c64955ce6d9","tid":433028,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:55:21.000Z","msg":"英國埃塞克斯郡一間咖啡店的助理經理，在店舖廚房見到一名員工「手部有所動作」，最初還以為同事竟然大膽到在工作期間手淫，但最後才發現自己擺了一個大烏龍。<br />\n<br />\n咖啡店關門後，25歲助理經理特納（Jade Turner）與20歲同事馬丁（Chris Martin）留下清潔。特納走入廚房時，看到馬丁背對着她弓著腰，而且手部有激烈動作，誤會他在手淫。她立即質問他在做甚麼，當馬丁轉身，才發現他只是在用力拭擦一個不銹鋼杯。<br />\n<br />\n特納憶述：「我（當時）很震驚，但很快便確定並非如我所想，就馬丁來說，任何事都有可能。」馬丁則說﹕「特納走入廚房說『你在幹甚麼，馬丁？』我在工作時確實『淘氣』一點，但我難以相信她竟會以為我正在做這種事。」<br />\n<br />\n馬丁雖然被誤會但毫不介意，他稱與特納已一起工作7個月，大讚對方很有幽默感，兩人都覺得這件事很好笑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171011/large/1507715502_db63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171011%2Flarge%2F1507715502_db63.jpg&h=14cfc736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57319441&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57319441%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171012&d=vTUh6qg%2FyzalzcvcFYk7ygEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=cf30789c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57319441%26category_guid%3D10793140%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171012&h=830e75bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57319441&amp;category_guid=10793140&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171012</a>"},{"pid":"e6129851fc4ebe974178a8c04b681b06c2524259","tid":433028,"uid":50041,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T04:58:33.000Z","msg":"點解咁都做到新聞"},{"pid":"1d9ec235ada0f4c1ff061